    7.  FAQ
    -------
        1) What does aplot stand for?
            amish's plot (I'm not too creative...)

        2) What file formats does aplot use?
            ...see dataio library...

        3) What wacky indent style did you use?
            Hey, I have very large monitors, and like small fonts.
            I don't care if my code is more than 80 chars wide.
            I really dislike:
                for (i=0; i < 10; i++) {
                    /* do something */
                }
            I really prefer:
                for (i=0; i < 10; i++)
                {
                    /* do something */
                }
            I use 4 character width tabs.
            And by the way, vile/xvile is the editor of kings.

